cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the learning dynamics of deep neural networks (DNNs) and proposes a layer-wise conditioning analysis to explore the optimization landscape with respect to each layer independently. This analysis is relevant to the field of machine learning, specifically in the sub-categories of deep learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on DNNs and their learning dynamics, the sub-categories of deep learning and neural networks are the most likely ones.
